Log in to the application using the Client Admin account.

Select the "View Study" option to view the study details.

Click on the "Documents" tab.

Manually append ?viewAs=client-manager to the URL to enable the Upload Document functionality.

It was observed that the document upload was successful, and the file was imported into the application.


Validate user roles and permissions server-side for every sensitive action such as uploading documents.

Remove or secure any impersonation/debug parameters like ?viewAs=client-manager to prevent unauthorized role switching.

Ensure that UI elements and backend endpoints are both governed by strict role-based access control (RBAC).
